# net-sriov-tools

```
PXVIRT SR-IOV Network Interface Card Manager

Usage: net-sriov-tools [COMMAND]

Commands:
  list    List SR-IOV capable network interfaces
  create  Create SR-IOV devices for a network interface
  save    Save the current configuration of all SR-IOV capable network interfaces
  load    Load SR-IOV configurations from /etc/network/sriov.d and apply them
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help     Print help
  -V, --version  Print version
```

Remember save conf.